    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small round or oval openings, such as windows in a wall or openings in the crown of a dome. For the design motif in the shape of an eye, use "eyes."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
